AVIATION SAFETY NOTICE

This project involves modifications to aircraft systems. Installation requires
compliance with applicable FAA regulations including 14 CFR Part 21.303 (owner-
produced parts) and requires a signed FAA Form 337 from an IA (Inspection
Authorization holder) before the aircraft is returned to service.

The software and hardware designs in this repository are provided for educational
and owner-builder purposes. The contributors make no warranty of airworthiness.
The owner/builder and their IA bear full responsibility for determining
airworthiness of any installation.

This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or approved by Beechcraft,
Textron Aviation, Airborne Electronics, or the FAA.
